      "text": "（いろいろと悩んでたけど、成長して）\n（ちゃんと前に進めたみたいだな。良かった）",
      "startTime": 238.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
