      "text": "嬉しいです",
      "startTime": 261.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_03-ktn031.m4a",
      "text": "渚なんて「家宝にするよ～」って、保存用に2冊\n観賞用に1冊、布教用に5冊買ってました",
      "startTime": 268.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "さすがだな……\n琴乃は今回の仕事をやってみてどうだった？",
      "startTime": 276.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_03-ktn032.m4a",
      "text": "悩んでる間は大変でしたけど……楽しかったです",
      "startTime": 279.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_03-ktn033.m4a",
      "text": "それに、結婚もいいかもって思いました",
      "startTime": 284.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_03-ktn034.m4a",
      "text": "でも……私はもっと先でいいですね",
      "startTime": 289.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_04_03-ktn035.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく今は、月ストのみんなと\nトップアイドルへの道を突き進みたいんです",
      "startTime": 297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
